<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>أثر الوالدة | Athar Alwalda</title>
    <!-- Google Fonts for professional typography -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Amiri&family=Tajawal:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root { --primary-color: #1b4332; --gold-accent: #d4af37; --light-bg: #f8f9fa; }
        body { font-family: 'Tajawal', sans-serif; margin: 0; background-color: var(--light-bg); }
        
        /* Navigation Bar */
        nav { background: white; padding: 1rem 5%; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        .logo { font-family: 'Amiri', serif; font-size: 1.8rem; color: var(--primary-color); font-weight: bold; }

        /* Hero Section */
        header { background: linear-gradient(rgba(27,67,50,0.8), rgba(27,67,50,0.8)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1542810634-71277d95dcbb?q=80&w=2070') center/cover;
                 height: 400px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; color: white; text-align: center; }
        
        .btn { background: var(--gold-accent); color: #222; padding: 12px 30px; border-radius: 5px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 20px; transition: 0.3s; }
        .btn:hover { background: white; color: var(--primary-color); }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav>
        <div class="logo">أثر الوالدة</div>
        <div>Professional Islamic Library</div>
    </nav>

    <header>
        <h1>مرحباً بكم في أثر الوالدة</h1>
        <p>بوابتكم للمراجع الإسلامية الموثوقة والعلوم النافعة</p>
        <a href="#links" class="btn">تصفح المكتبة</a>
    </header>

</body>
</html>
